=E2=80=A6 known as Roaring Kitty =E2=80=94=C2=A0tweeted a drawing of a guy =
leaning forward in a chair. This sparked a huge rally in GameStop shares fo=
r no particular reason. (At no point did Gill tweet=C2=A0about GameStop; he=
