sed at $48.75 on May 14, and over the last two weeks =E2=80=94=C2=A0May 13 =
through May 24 =E2=80=94=C2=A0the average closing price has been $27.23 per=
 share.GameStop, not being dummies, took the opportunity to launch an at-th=
