ue. Given this very particular skill that he has =E2=80=94 the ability to a=
dd billions of dollars of value to, at least, this stock, with essentially =
no effort =E2=80=94 what is the best way for him to monetize it? What is th=
e highest-value use that financial markets could find for Keith Gill?If you=
 were [GameStop Chief Executive Officer] Ryan Cohen, would you hire Gill to=
 run GameStop=E2=80=99s investor relations?=C2=A0I guess I will shrug and p=
oint to those questions again? If you were GameStop, how much would you hav=
